				<xsd:annotation>
					<xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">The Tax element contains any tax information such as the taxable amounts and the tax codes.  It is optional and used to summarize tax amounts across all the document lines. The principal intent of this data type is for use as a memo item</xsd:documentation>
